name: 天賜法帽用
note:
<Custom Initiate Effect>
if (this.isSkill()) {
  var item = this.item();
  
  // 判定 1：檢查「傷害類型」選單 (3: HP恢復, 4: MP恢復)
  var isDamageHeal = (item.damage.type === 3 || item.damage.type === 4);
  
  // 判定 2：檢查「效果」列表 (11: HP恢復, 12: MP恢復)
  var isEffectHeal = item.effects.some(function(e) {
    return e.code === 11 || e.code === 12;
  });
  if (isDamageHeal || isEffectHeal) {
    // 增加一次重複次數
    this._repeatsModifier = (this._repeatsModifier || 0) + 1;
    this.makeTargets(); 
    user.refresh();
  }
}
</Custom Initiate Effect>
<notClearedWhenDead>

name: 魔法連發
note:
<Custom Establish Effect>
var skill = this.item();
if (skill) {
  if (this.isMagical() && skill.stypeId !== 20 && !this._isExtraAction && !user._isAutoSkillExecuting && !this._hasTriggeredExtra) {
    this._hasTriggeredExtra = true;
    // 4. 機率判定 25%
    if (Math.random() < 0.25) {
      var cost = user.skillMpCost(skill);
      if (user.mp >= cost) {
        user.paySkillCost(skill);
        user.forceAction(skill.id, target.index());
        var nextAct = user.currentAction();
        if (nextAct) {
           nextAct._isExtraAction = true;
        }       
        BattleManager.forceAction(user);
        user.startAnimation(119);
        if (SceneManager._scene._logWindow) {
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</Custom Establish Effect>
<notClearedWhenDead>
